    <title>python爬虫爬取豆瓣Top250</title>
    <link href="https://shmoriarty.github.io/2018/12/28/2018-12-28-python%E7%88%AC%E8%99%AB%E7%88%AC%E5%8F%96%E8%B1%86%E7%93%A3Top250/"/>
    <id>https://shmoriarty.github.io/2018/12/28/2018-12-28-python爬虫爬取豆瓣Top250/</id>
    <published>2018-12-28T06:17:07.000Z</published>
    <updated>2019-03-01T04:55:05.897Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>目标:爬取豆瓣Top250数据(这里只是学习)<a id="more"></a></p><h2 id="创建Scrapy项目"><a href="#创建Scrapy项目" class="headerlink" title="创建Scrapy项目"></a>创建Scrapy项目</h2><p>这里使用的是python的一个爬虫框架<a href="https://github.com/scrapy/scrapy" target="_blank" rel="noopener">scrapy</a></p><p>在cmd里使用下面命令安装scrapy</p><figure class="highlight cmd"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">pip install scrapy</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>使用下面的命令创建项目</p><figure class="highlight cmd"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">scrapy startproject douban</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="编写items文件-根据需要爬取的内容来定义字段"><a href="#编写items文件-根据需要爬取的内容来定义字段" class="headerlink" title="编写items文件(根据需要爬取的内容来定义字段)"></a>编写items文件(根据需要爬取的内容来定义字段)</h2><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> scrapy</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">DoubanItem</span><span class="params">(scrapy.Item)</span>:</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment"># define the fields for your item here like:</span></span><br><span class="line">    name = scrapy.Field()  <span class="comment"># 电影名称</span></span><br><span class="line">    top = scrapy.Field()  <span class="comment"># 电影排名</span></span><br><span class="line">    rating_num = scrapy.Field()  <span class="comment"># 电影评分</span></span><br><span class="line">    rating_sum = scrapy.Field()  <span class="comment"># 电影评价人数</span></span><br><span class="line">    inq = scrapy.Field()  <span class="comment"># 简介</span></span><br><span class="line">    url = scrapy.Field()  <span class="comment"># url</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="编写爬虫文件"><a href="#编写爬虫文件" class="headerlink" title="编写爬虫文件"></a>编写爬虫文件</h2><p>在douban豆瓣目录下创建基础爬虫类DouBanSpider.py</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> scrapy</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> douban.items <span class="keyword">import</span> DoubanItem</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">DouBanSpider</span><span class="params">(scrapy.Spider)</span>:</span></span><br><span class="line">    name = <span class="string">'douban'</span></span><br><span class="line">    allowed_domains = []</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">start_requests</span><span class="params">(self)</span>:</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">for</span> i <span class="keyword">in</span> range(<span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">10</span>):</span><br><span class="line">            s = str(i * <span class="number">25</span>)</span><br><span class="line">            url = <span class="string">'https://movie.douban.com/top250?start='</span> + s</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">yield</span> scrapy.Request(url, callback=self.parse)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">parse</span><span class="params">(self, response)</span>:</span></span><br><span class="line">        movies = response.xpath(<span class="string">"//div[starts-with(@class, 'item')]"</span>)</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">for</span> m <span class="keyword">in</span> range(<span class="number">0</span>, len(movies)):</span><br><span class="line">            item = DoubanItem()</span><br><span class="line">            item[<span class="string">'url'</span>] = movies.xpath(<span class="string">".//div/div/a/@href"</span>).extract()[m]</span><br><span class="line">            item[<span class="string">'top'</span>] = movies.xpath(<span class="string">".//div/em/text()"</span>).extract()[m]</span><br><span class="line">            item[<span class="string">'name'</span>] = movies.xpath(<span class="string">".//div/div/a/span[1]/text()"</span>).extract()[m]</span><br><span class="line">            item[<span class="string">'rating_num'</span>] = movies.xpath(<span class="string">".//div/div/div/span[contains(@class,'rating_num')]/text()"</span>).extract()[m]</span><br><span class="line">            item[<span class="string">'rating_sum'</span>] = movies.xpath(<span class="string">".//div/div/div/span[4]/text()"</span>).extract()[m]</span><br><span class="line">            item[<span class="string">'inq'</span>] = movies.xpath(<span class="string">".//p[contains(@class,'quote')]/span/text()"</span>).extract()[m]</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">yield</span> item</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>这里start_requests是请求页面数据，如果不写是根据你定义的start_urls 来进行请求，callback默认是parse方法。parse方法是做html的解析和二次请求，不过这里没有做二次请求。</p><p>具体的html解析这里是使用了xpath选择器，当然还有css选择器，不过这里没有使用到。</p><p>修改settings.py文件设置header</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 设置请求头部，添加url</span></span><br><span class="line">DEFAULT_REQUEST_HEADERS = &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">"User-Agent"</span>: <span class="string">"Mozilla/5.0 (compatible; MSIE 9.0; Windows NT 6.1; Trident/5.0;"</span>,</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">'Accept'</span>: <span class="string">'text/html,application/xhtml+xml,application/xml;q=0.9,*/*;q=0.8'</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>运行<code>scrapy crawl douban -o douban.csv</code>之后就会发现在douban目录下多了一个douban.csv文件，里面是我们爬出的数据</p><h2 id="存入数据库"><a href="#存入数据库" class="headerlink" title="存入数据库"></a>存入数据库</h2><p>当然我们想要的不是csv文件，一般都是想要将数据存入数据库，scrapy也支持存入数据库。首先安装pymysql执行命令<code>pip install pymysql</code>，然后打开pipelines.py编写代码：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> pymysql</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">DoubanPipeline</span><span class="params">(object)</span>:</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">__init__</span><span class="params">(self)</span>:</span></span><br><span class="line">        self.conn = pymysql.connect(host=<span class="string">'你的host'</span>, user=<span class="string">'用户名'</span>, passwd=<span class="string">'密码'</span>, db=<span class="string">'数据库'</span>)</span><br><span class="line">        self.cursor = self.conn.cursor()</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">process_item</span><span class="params">(self, item, spider)</span>:</span></span><br><span class="line">        title = item[<span class="string">'name'</span>].strip()</span><br><span class="line">        top = item[<span class="string">'top'</span>].strip()</span><br><span class="line">        rating_num = item[<span class="string">'rating_num'</span>].strip()</span><br><span class="line">        rating_sum = item[<span class="string">'rating_sum'</span>].strip()</span><br><span class="line">        inq = item[<span class="string">'inq'</span>].strip()</span><br><span class="line">        url = item[<span class="string">'url'</span>].strip()</span><br><span class="line">        sql = <span class="string">'insert into douban250(movie_name,rating_num,rating_sum,top_no,inq,url) VALUES (%s,%s,%s,%s,%s,%s)'</span></span><br><span class="line">        self.cursor.execute(sql, (title, rating_num, rating_sum, top, inq, url))</span><br><span class="line">        self.conn.commit()</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> item</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>修改settings.py</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ITEM_PIPELINES = &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">'douban.pipelines.DoubanPipeline'</span>: <span class="number">300</span>,</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>一个爬虫项目可以有多个管道，后面所跟着的数字是指这个管道的优先级。</p><p>然后再运行<code>scrapy crawl douban</code>等待运行完成就会发现数据里有豆瓣Top250的数据了。</p><p>scrapy还可以使用代理ip防止单个ip多次请求ip被ban的情况，这里就不多做赘述了。</p>]]></content>
    
    <summary type="html">
    
      &lt;p&gt;目标:爬取豆瓣Top250数据(这里只是学习)
    
    </summary>
    
